<p source="SHANGBO.JINGGONGNUE 6.30.1 (STRIPS 1-2) MACHENGYUAN 6: 162, 166 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-1a.1">齊景公疥且瘧,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-1a.2">逾歲不已.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-1a.3">會譴與梁丘據言於公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-1a.4">“吾幣帛甚美</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-1a.5">於吾先君之量矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-1a.6">吾珪璧大</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-1a.7">於吾先君之[1] [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-1a.8">[...] 公疥且瘧,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-1a.9">逾歲不已,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-1a.10">是吾無良祝, 史也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-1a.11">吾欲誅諸祝,史.”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGGONGNUE 6.30.2 (STRIPS 2-3) MACHENGYUAN 6: 166, 169 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-2a.1">公舉首答之:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-2a.2">“倘然,是吾所望於汝也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-2a.3">盍誅之.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-2a.4">二子將 [2] [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-2a.5">[...]是言也.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-2a.6">高子, 國子答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-2a.7">“身為親,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-2a.8">又何愛焉?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-2a.9">是信吾無良祝,史,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-2a.10">公盍誅之.”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGGONGNUE 6.30.3 (STRIPS 3-4) MACHENGYUAN 6: 169, 171 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-3a.1">晏子夕,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-3a.2">二大夫退.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-3a.3">公入晏子而告之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-3a.4">若其告高子[3]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-3a.5">[...] “屈木為成于宋,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-3a.6">王命屈木</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-3a.7">問范武子之行焉.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGGONGNUE 6.30.4 (STRIP 4) MACHENGYUAN 6: 171 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-4a.1">文子答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-4a.2">‘夫子使其私吏</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-4a.3">聽獄于晉邦,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-4a.4">溥 (迫) 情而不逾 (偷),</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-4a.5">使其私祝, 史進[4] [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGGONGNUE 6.30.5 (STRIP 5) MACHENGYUAN 6: 174 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-5a" ed="tls" n="001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-5a.1">[...] 蘊聖,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-5a.2">外內不廢,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-5a.3">可因於民者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-5a.4">其祝, 史之為其君祝敚(說)也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-5a.5">正 [言][5] [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGGONGNUE 6.30.6 (STRIP 7) MACHENGYUAN 6: 178 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-6a" ed="tls" n="001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-6a.1">[...]君祝敚(說),</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-6a.2">毋(如)尃(=陳) 情</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-6a.3">忍罪乎,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-6a.4">則言不聽,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-6a.5">情不獲.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-6a.6">如順言</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-6a.7">弇惡乎,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-6a.8">則恐後誅于史者.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-6a.9">故其祝, 史制篾篿折祝之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-6a.10">多愚言 [7] [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGGONGNUE 6.30.7 (STRIP 9) MACHENGYUAN 6: 183 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-7a" ed="tls" n="001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-7a.1">[...] 明德觀行,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-7a.2">物而祟者也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-7a.3">非為美玉肴牲也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-7a.4">今內寵有割X (??),</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-7a.5">外亦有梁丘</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-7a.6">據營誑.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-7a.7">公退(納)武夫,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-7a.8">惡聖人,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-7a.9">播浧(盈)藏篤,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-7a.10">使[9] [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGGONGNUE 6.30.8 (STRIP 6) MACHENGYUAN 6: 176 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-8a" ed="tls" n="001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-8a.1">[...]亡矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-8a.2">而揚清者與得萬福焉.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-8a.3">今君之貪昏</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-8a.4">苛慝,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-8a.5">辟違[6] [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGGONGNUE 6.30.9 (STRIP 8) MACHENGYUAN 6: 180 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-9a" ed="tls" n="001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-9a.1">[...]詛為無傷,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-9a.2">祝亦無益.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-9a.3">今薪蒸</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-9a.4">使虞守之;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-9a.5">澤梁</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-9a.6">使守之;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-9a.7">山林</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-9a.8">使衡守之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-9a.9">舉邦為欽禁,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-9a.10">約挾諸關,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-9a.11">縛 ￼ (纓)諸市.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-9a.12">眾[8] [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGGONGNUE 6.30.10 (STRIP 11) MACHENGYUAN 6: 186 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-10a" ed="tls" n="001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-10a.1">其左右相頌自善曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-10a.2">‘蓋必死,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-10a.3">偷為樂乎.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-10a.4">故死期將至,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-10a.5">何仁 [11]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGGONGNUE 6.30.11 (STRIPS 10, 12) MACHENGYUAN 6: 185, 187 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-11a" ed="tls" n="001-11a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-11a.1">故內寵之妾,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-11a.2">迫奪于國,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-11a.3">外寵之臣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-11a.4">出矯於鄙.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-11a.5">自姑,尤以西,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-11a.6">聊,攝以東,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-11a.7">其人數多已,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-11a.8">是皆貧苦約疾,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-11a.9">夫婦皆詛,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-11a.10">一丈夫執尋之幣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-11a.11">三布之玉,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-11a.12">雖是夫 [10] [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-11a.13">二夫何不受皇X(?),</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-11a.14">則未得與聞.”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGGONGNUE 6.30.12 (STRIPS 12-13) MACHENGYUAN 6: 187, 188 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-12a" ed="tls" n="001-12a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-12a.1">[...] 公強起,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-12a.2">違席曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-12a.3">“善哉吾子!”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-12a.4">晏子:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-12a.5">“是襄桓之言也!”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-12a.6">“祭,貞不獲祟,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-12a.7">以至於此.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-12a.8">神見吾淫暴 [12].</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-12a.9">[...]請祭與貞.”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGGONGNUE 6.30.13 (STRIP 13) MACHENGYUAN 6: 188 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-13a" ed="tls" n="001-13a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-13a.1">晏子辭.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-13a.2">公或謂之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-13a.3">晏子許諾.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-13a.4">命割 (??)不敢監祭,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-13a.5">梁丘據不敢監貞.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0059_tls_001-13a.6">旬又五,公乃出見折. [13]</seg></p>

